cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink carrier bandwidth to an excessively high value of 1000 PRBs will cause invalid configuration and cell setup failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行載波帶寬設定為過高的 1000 PRB 值會導致無效配置，並造成小區設置失敗。
